query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stats')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('autocorrelation',
'descriptive-statistics',
'expected-value',
'experiment-design',
'interaction',
'interpretation',
'mean',
'optimization',
'pdf',
'poisson-distribution',
'random-variable',
'simulation',
'spss',
'survival',
'terminology');
